# J&R Games Buylist Application

This is a Next.js 15 application for J&R Games buylist management. The app allows users to browse gaming items with filtering capabilities and provides an admin interface for managing items, categories, and console types.

## Tech Stack
- **Framework**: Next.js 15 with App Router
- **Database**: PostgreSQL with Prisma ORM
- **Authentication**: NextAuth.js with credentials provider
- **Styling**: Tailwind CSS
- **Icons**: Lucide React
- **Notifications**: React Hot Toast

## Key Features
- Public item browsing with search and filtering
- Admin dashboard for CRUD operations
- Console type and console management
- Category management
- Image support for items
- Responsive design

